SubmitterDescription.SubmitterName: International Standards For Cytogenomic Arrays Consortium (ISCA)

SampleDescription.Description: a supernumerary ring chromosome derived from chromosome 5 was observed in 45.0% and 48.5% of interphase nuclei from a direct preparation and PHA-stimulated culture, respectively. Phenotype: prominent forehead, large protruding occiput, hypoplastic jaw, macrocephaly, dysmorphic facial features, hypothyroidism
